snippet.title: Cyber Grannies (1997) Intro Animation
snippet.description: If you're expecting a social networking site for grandmothers, elderly cam girls or teachers who use Skype to teach Indians, this is neither of those things. The titular grannies are personifications of the 26 letters of the alphabet, each with an occupation and first name starting with a certain letter. I was just as curious as you were when I found this within my collection of old Mac software, and now that I can emulate it on my current computer, I bring you one of the catchiest theme songs ever recorded for a children's game.
